rows.label: tlk41300012_04_msg0001
rows.name:
You're the ones who caught former
Chairman Bahn's dad, aren't you?

rows.label: tlk41300012_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Not even the SAB could get a hold
of that slimeball.

rows.label: tlk41300012_04_msg0004
rows.name:
But still, he wasn't completely
heartless. I think he softened up
a little after his son was born.

rows.label: tlk41300012_04_msg0005
rows.name:
And the two of them did make the
guild what it is today. I wonder what's
going to become of it now...?
